== 產地 ==
主要產地為[[馬達加斯加|馬達加斯加]]，但礦床早已開採殆盡，除此之外在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]及緬甸亦有草莓綠柱石產出。<ref>{{cite journal en |author = Hänni H.A., Krzemnicki M.S.|year = 2003 |title = Caesium-rich morganite from Afghanistan and Madagascar |journal = Journal of Gemmology |volume = 28 |issue = 7 |pages = 417 - 429}}</ref>

